com.samskivert.depot.expression

Class FluentExp<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.samskivert.depot.expression.FluentExp<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SQLExpression<T>, SQLFragment
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ColumnExp, FullText.Match, FullText.Rank

    public abstract class FluentExp<T>
extends Object
implements SQLExpression<T>
    Provides a fluent API for creating most SQL expressions like and, or, equal, not equal, etc.
